name: Stagnant Star
description:
It appears one of the seedlings has come to a stand still, almost as though it's preparing for another change, maybe it's place of home is too small for it to survive now. 

Frequency lays calm in a cap full of water captured by the reflection of light.  

My research has been stagnant for a while as I have been working on the cross over of my cymamtic art and VR sculpting. Water, light, sound reflects the secrets of the universe.
